<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>404 - Página no encontrada | Area Técnico Profesional</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
  <div class="not-found-wrapper">
    <header class="header">
      <nav class="navbar container">
        <div class="navbar-brand">
          <a href="/" class="logo-link">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M22 10v6M2 10l10-5 10 5-10 5z"/>
              <path d="M6 12v5c3 3 9 3 12 0v-5"/>
            </svg>
            <span class="logo-text">Area Técnico Profesional</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </nav>
    </header>

    <main class="not-found">
      <div class="not-found-content">
        <div class="not-found-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="80" height="80" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/>
            <path d="M16 16s-1.5-2-4-2-4 2-4 2"/>
            <line x1="9" y1="9" x2="9.01" y2="9"/>
            <line x1="15" y1="9" x2="15.01" y2="9"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h1>404</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">Ups! Esta página no existe</p>
        <p class="description">
          La página que buscas no se encuentra disponible.<br/>
          Es posible que el enlace esté roto o la dirección sea incorrecta.
        </p>
        <div class="not-found-actions">
          <a href="/" class="btn btn-primary">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M3 9l9-7 9 7v11a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2z"/>
              <polyline points="9 22 9 12 15 12 15 22"/>
            </svg>
            Volver al inicio
          </a>
          <a href="/noticias/" class="btn btn-secondary">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M4 22h16a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V4a2 2 0 0 0-2-2H8a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 1-2 2Zm0 0a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-9c0-1.1.9-2 2-2h2"/>
            </svg>
            Ver noticias
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>
  </div>

  <style>
    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8fafc 0%, #f1f5f9 100%);
      min-height: 100vh;
      color: #1e293b;
    }

    @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
      body {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f172a 0%, #1e293b 100%);
        color: #f1f5f9;
      }
    }

    .header {
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 100;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);
      backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
      .header {
        background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.92);
        border-bottom-color: #334155;
      }
    }

    .navbar {
      max-width: 1400px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 2rem;
      height: 60px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .navbar-brand {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .logo-link {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.75rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #1e293b;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .logo-link svg {
      color: #15803d;
    }

    @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
      .logo-link {
        color: #f1f5f9;
      }
      .logo-link svg {
        color: #4ade80;
      }
    }

    .not-found-wrapper {
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .not-found {
      flex: 1;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 4rem 2rem;
    }

    .not-found-content {
      text-align: center;
      max-width: 480px;
      animation: fadeInUp 0.5s ease-out;
    }

    @keyframes fadeInUp {
      from {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(20px);
      }
      to {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(0);
      }
    }

    .not-found-icon {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      width: 120px;
      height: 120px;
      background: rgba(22, 163, 74, 0.1);
      border-radius: 50%;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      color: #15803d;
    }

    @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
      .not-found-icon {
        background: rgba(74, 222, 128, 0.15);
        color: #4ade80;
      }
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 5rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #15803d, #22c55e);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
      margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
      line-height: 1;
    }

    .subtitle {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #1e293b;
      margin: 0 0 1rem;
    }

    @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
      .subtitle {
        color: #f1f5f9;
      }
    }

    .description {
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: #64748b;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin: 0 0 2rem;
    }

    @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
      .description {
        color: #94a3b8;
      }
    }

    .not-found-actions {
      display: flex;
      gap: 1rem;
      justify-content: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
      font-size: 0.9375rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 10px;
      transition: all 0.2s;
    }

    .btn-primary {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #15803d, #16a34a);
      color: white;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(22, 163, 74, 0.3);
    }

    .btn-primary:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 6px 16px rgba(22, 163, 74, 0.4);
    }

    .btn-secondary {
      background: white;
      color: #1e293b;
      border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
    }

    @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
      .btn-secondary {
        background: #1e293b;
        color: #f1f5f9;
        border-color: #334155;
      }
    }

    .btn-secondary:hover {
      border-color: #15803d;
      color: #15803d;
      background: rgba(22, 163, 74, 0.08);
    }

    @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
      .btn-secondary:hover {
        color: #4ade80;
        border-color: #4ade80;
        background: rgba(74, 222, 128, 0.12);
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 480px) {
      h1 {
        font-size: 4rem;
      }

      .not-found-actions {
        flex-direction: column;
      }

      .btn {
        width: 100%;
        justify-content: center;
      }
    }
  </style>
</body>
</html>